                  </persName>
            . I am a pawnbroker, and live in Strutton-ground, Westminster. These two waistcoats were pawned by the prisoner, in the afternoon of the 26th of July.(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>The prisoner received an excellent character.</p>
